  "description": "Kotencotenco is a gag strip anime for young children featuring the flourishes of the Prince of the country of the Paradice, Kotenco.<br><br>\nKotenco guards the &ldquo;Angel Star&rdquo; for the Queen in the Paradice. Kotenco is a very good child, but when the bad spirits rise, Kotenco transforms into Matenco. Unlike Kotenco, Matenco is a very naughty child and troubles everyone. But don't worry! By changing the angel ring, Matenco goes back to being Kotenco. Will Kotenco be able to guard the &ldquo;Angel Star&rdquo; from the ruler and the Devil of the Country of the Ground, who is aiming for the Paradice? ",
